The evidence with the title 'What liberals get wrong about single payer - The Washington Post ' says Jan 13, 2014  ... The Swiss and Dutch health systems look a lot like Obamacare 's health- insurance exchanges. In France, about 90 percent of citizens have supplementary health insurance . Sweden has moved from a single-payer system to one with private insurers . Yet all these countries pay vastly less for drugs, surgeries  ... 
